message.body: I heard nicks grandma died, is there a viewing or anything coming up?
Oh shit! I didn't even hear. When did you find out?
Sandy told me today. Vivas said theres a viewing Wed night, not sure when
Oh man. Yeah I'll see if I can get details.
The call time will be pretty early tomm. I'll let you know later when they tell me
I think I'm just going to take the subway up in a few, I need to relax for a bit. See you there
good dealman. See yah in a bit.
You want to work a commercial tomm art dept. $300/day let me know ASAP. Thanks
